386afdfc9adc4452ac8717","tid":1954970,"uid":112702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:45:20.000Z","msg":"洲際喎<br />\n認真咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e2f3e57965a0f46c80d9a06efa761ceacbbf02","tid":1954970,"uid":187938,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:47:12.000Z","msg":"等睇新聞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58e59b1583cc91bc5828075bd03ec9f6c91cac6","tid":1954970,"uid":265943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:47:55.000Z","msg":"真5真呀，高級客棧"},{"pid":"e79cc5e934be5f279fb3c68369556277b55197e3","tid":1954970,"uid":276821,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:48:29.000Z","msg":"唔撚po 01 link<br />\n<br />\n「新冠肺炎」疫情下，訪港旅客大減，不少酒店都宣布員工放無薪假，或暫停營業，最新有消息指，洲際酒店將於本月20日提早進行裝修，為期30個月，並會遣散所有員工。<br />\n<br />\n有香港洲際酒店員工向《香港01》透露，酒店今日（2日）舉行員工大會，並宣布上述決定。據了解，最後上班日期為5月1日「勞動節」；5年以下資歷的員工獲1個月薪金賠償，5至10年獲賠償2個月薪金；10至15年獲賠償3個月薪金；15年以上則獲4個月人工。<br />\n<br />\n記者到酒店的官方網站嘗試訂房，發現4月20日之後的房間已沒法預訂，之後亦曾致電洲際酒店公關部查詢詳情，惟截稿前未得到回覆。至於酒店工會回覆指，仍在了解事件，暫未收到求助個案。"},{"pid":"9aef5cb2d65531a52d8e53950384d3581170bc4e","tid":1954970,"uid":214502,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjdkecB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjdkecB.jpg&h=d91d541d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bd3a4ffd3d79cd718b1c3fde1e94c2d0e2386fd","tid":1954970,"uid":120955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:51:35.000Z","msg":"好耐之前就講佢大裝修架啦"},{"pid":"ecf537378257b6cb3e97ef7ca774a17ac5e960c2","tid":1954970,"uid":24356,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T09:04:46.000Z","msg":"裝修啊 改名做返麗晶大酒店"},{"pid":"15779202a2fba6b5d2dda005a01c6b4952d87b32","tid":1954970,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,